{"tid":2310880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊憂疑犯模仿許智峯做法　籲法庭處理案件需小心 形容遣返安排 香港已經「無嘢可以做到」","createTime":"2020-12-03T14:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T02:43:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":57,"dislike":416,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"986a16c487f00f025f31c95629c29344e8baf08b","tid":2310880,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員許智峯表示將會正式流亡，退出民主黨，暫別香港。行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊指，近期類似案件的疑犯，選擇棄保潛逃的比例相當高，擔心今次事件會出現模仿效應，認為法庭在處理類似案件時要更小心。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊表示，香港與世界各地移交疑犯的協議差不多已經不存在，增加了疑犯棄保潛逃的誘因。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港能否申請遣返許智峯，湯家驊認為，機會相當低，因為根據聯合國指引，政治罪行案件或疑犯有政治背景，都不能移交，湯家驊形容香港已經「無嘢可以做到」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563449-20201203.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563449-20201203.htm&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=c1d28c6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563449-20201203.htm&h=8ddbb89a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563449-20201203.htm</a>"},{"pid":"32b74bcd570b3c9910d98f0c746f2c897a3452f6","tid":2310880,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58554692872f9aa989cf0735ccfa8ce597c5ed89","tid":2310880,"uid":37874,"like":307,"dislike":2,"score":305,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:47:43.000Z","msg":"因為根據聯合國指引，政治罪行案件或疑犯有政治背景，都不能移交 <br />\n國安法又好 刑事都好 邊隻眼見到關政治事<br />\n十一哥你講乜撚野 同港府作對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad23f5acc211b68c0ffe6393efea23c56f43236","tid":2310880,"uid":34869,"like":456,"dislike":5,"score":451,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:48:13.00